flowchart TD
    A[Caller or Schedule] --> B[Logic Apps Standard<br/>Parent Agent Loop]
    B --> C{Should approved tool be called?}
    C -- No --> D[Return: capability not available]
    C -- Yes --> E[Tool: Call workflow in this logic app]
    E --> F[Child Workflow Tool Boundary]
    F --> G[Call Azure Function-based PEP<br/>Managed Identity + Entra ID]
    G --> H{PEP allow?}
    H -- No --> I[Fail Closed<br/>Return Denial]
    H -- Failed / Timeout / Malformed --> J[Fail Closed<br/>PEP Failure Denial]
    H -- Yes --> K[Azure Monitor Logs Connector<br/>Managed Identity + RBAC]
    K --> L[Log Analytics Workspace<br/>Fixed Query Only]
    L --> M[Return Success to Agent Loop]

    subgraph Private_Network["Private Azure Network Boundary"]
        B
        E
        F
        G
        K
        L
    end
